CustomField.description: Determines which tab (Bio Demo, Gift Processing, Interim, Review Transaction (v2)) is active when Knowtify modal is opened. If blank, use the enabled tab field (Enable Bio Demo Tab, Enable Gift Processing Tab, Enable Interim Tab, Enable Review Transaction (v2) Tab) based on the specified context.
